{"tid":1742894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人黎緊幾日既日程表","createTime":"2019-11-21T03:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T00:26:22.000Z","uid":212819,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9b927ae1c5f08a6debc8bfa993f35c4d8840f237","tid":1742894,"uid":212819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"星期四（今日）<br />\n 1. 和理非地區集氣活動（各大商場為區選做勢）<br />\n 2. 重整連儂牆（幫區選做文宣、煲大催淚彈後遺症及simon事件、加強宣傳「黎明行動」既目的係攬炒經濟）<br />\n3. 為黎明行動重整旗鼓（討論行動成效、點樣分配塞路塞鐵人手、點樣可以令市民知道行動目的...）<br />\n<br />\n星期五<br />\n如上<br />\n<br />\n星期六<br />\n如上<br />\n<br />\n星期日<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">早起去投票 咩都唔洗做 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">記住要靜靜地贏！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n星期一<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">再次黎明行動！黎一波比上兩星期更有效既不合作同埋堵路行動！記住要喺藍絲鬧手足既時候 手足解釋點解要咁做 而唔係咩都唔講俾人鬧/打 令行動不失民意</span><br />\n<br />\n同意既幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔同意既請提出意見"},{"pid":"e1d2e2671065158767fa55c7e486dd3db6c4a945","tid":1742894,"uid":212819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:37:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca2648fe960c593cb8edb311c83b3b11f5c0ab43","tid":1742894,"uid":212819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:37:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c297f781c6bd90b8a4f84e4ce41ee49fc32dabec","tid":1742894,"uid":212819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bd3eceab48fbcc915759dd3f593254a500637e6","tid":1742894,"uid":212819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:38:46.000Z","msg":"最緊要係討論 唔係拉或者話人帶風向"},{"pid":"f1ed7c9b3a49b489aadad8075340e1bafd311d95","tid":1742894,"uid":131770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:38:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d73af5489d88631ee352d535dd2fd6e85f51cb6b","tid":1742894,"uid":212819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:39:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53ec039c6dd526